            "body": "Sorry, but I don't see an actual compelling problem described here that would be within our scope to solve. If you want to use Vim regex outside of Nvim, you can already do that by writing standalone Lua scripts using `vim.regex` that can be run with `nvim -l script.lua` (or even `./script.lua` with the right shebang).",
